== 制作 ==
2013年6月，Starz宣布要为该题材拍摄一部于2013年11月开始制作的16集长的新剧。<ref name="Outlander Greenlighted">{{cite web|title=''Outlander'' Greenlighted To Series By Starz|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/06/outlander-greenlighted-to-series-by-starz/|accessdate=2013-07-16|date=2013-06-01|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|archive-date=2014-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140807131220/http://www.deadline.com/2013/06/outlander-greenlighted-to-series-by-starz/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Starz confirms">{{cite web|title=UPDATE:Starz Confirms ''Outlander'' Series Pickup|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/06/starz-confirms-outlander-series-pickup/|accessdate=2013-07-16|date=2013-06-25|work=Deadline.com|archive-date=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140708065658/http://www.deadline.com/2013/06/starz-confirms-outlander-series-pickup/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="DL130601">{{cite news|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/06/outlander-greenlighted-to-series-by-starz/|title=''Outlander'' Greenlighted To Series By Starz|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2013-06-01|accessdate=2014-07-31|archive-date=2014-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140807131220/http://www.deadline.com/2013/06/outlander-greenlighted-to-series-by-starz/|dead-url=no}}</ref>试播集播出后不久的2014年8月15日，电视台又为该剧续订了至少13集的拍摄计划。<ref name="EW 2nd Season 2014-08">{{cite web|title=''Outlander'' renewed for second season|url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2014/08/15/outlander-renewed-second-season/|accessdate=2014-08-15|date=2014-08-15|last=Hibberd|first=James|work=[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150118183114/http://insidetv.ew.com/2014/08/15/outlander-renewed-second-season/|archivedate=2015-01-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>而原作者加巴顿女士也将一直担任该剧顾问。<ref name="CordDiana">{{cite web|title=Diana Gabaldon returns with new ''Outlander'' book|url=http://www.azcentral.com/story/entertainment/books/2014/06/07/diana-gabaldon-returns-new-outlander-book/10042975/|accessdate=2014-07-31|date=2014-06-25|last=Cordova|first=Randy|work={{tsl|en|The Arizona Republic|The Arizona Republic}}}}</ref>担任创作者和监督人的门罗(Moore)表示，第一集“前30到40分钟里我们拍了很多书中没有的内容或是书中情节经过压缩后的内容。”他还表示不打算像一般的科幻剧那样把时间穿越的过程用大量特效展示出来。<ref name="EW Lee 2014-07">{{cite web|title=''Outlander'' Preview|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20835937,00.html|accessdate=2014-09-23|date=2014-07-18|last=Lee|first=Stephan|work=Entertainment Weekly|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129021041/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20835937,00.html|archivedate=2014-11-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 敲定角色 ===
2013年7月9日，Sam Heughan被敲定为剧中男性领袖Jamie Fraser的饰演者。<ref name="Update">{{cite web|title=UPDATE: Starz's ''Outlander'' Officially Names Sam Heughan As Lead|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/07/outlander-series-star-starz/|accessdate=2013-07-16|date=2013-07-09|publisher=Deadline.com|archive-date=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140708062018/http://www.deadline.com/2013/07/outlander-series-star-starz/|dead-url=no}}</ref>8月8日，第二个选定的演员是Tobias Menzies，在剧中饰演Frank和Jonathan Randall两位角色。<ref>{{cite web|title=Tobias Menzies Cast In Starz’s ''Outlander''|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/08/tobias-menzies-cast-in-starzs-outlander/|accessdate=2013-08-17|date=2013-08-08|publisher=Deadline.com|archive-date=2013-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110202008/http://www.deadline.com/2013/08/tobias-menzies-cast-in-starzs-outlander/|dead-url=no}}</ref>9月4日，Graham McTavish和Gary Lewis也加盟该剧。<ref>{{cite web|title=Starz’s ''Outlander'' Adds Two To Cast|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/09/starzs-outlander-adds-two-to-cast/|accessdate=2013-09-04|date=2013-09-04|publisher=Deadline.com|archive-date=2013-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014101919/http://www.deadline.com/2013/09/starzs-outlander-adds-two-to-cast/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年9月11日，爱尔兰演员{{link-en|凯特瑞娜·巴菲|Caitriona Balfe}}通过角色选拔，被敲定为该剧女主演Claire Beauchamp Randall的饰演者。<ref>{{cite web|title=''Super 8'''s Caitriona Balfe to Play Claire on Starz's ''Outlander''|url=http://www.thewrap.com/starz-outlander-claire-caitriona-balfe/|accessdate=2014-06-14|date=2013-09-11|work=The Wrap|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180905023230/https://www.thewrap.com/starz-outlander-claire-caitriona-balfe/|archivedate=2018-09-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>

原作者加巴顿女士也在第4集《The Gathering》中跑了个龙套，饰演了其中的Iona MacTavish。<ref>{{cite web|title=First Look: ''Outlander'' author Diana Gabaldon cameos on Starz series|url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2014/08/27/outlander-diana-gabaldon-cameo/|accessdate=2014-09-01|date=2014-08-27|last=Wilkinson|first=Amy|publisher=EW.com|archive-date=2014-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141216095537/http://insidetv.ew.com/2014/08/27/outlander-diana-gabaldon-cameo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年8月，{{link-en|弗拉泽·西内|Frazer Hines}}获悉也将出演将于2015年播出的某集，并在其中扮演一名[[典狱长|典狱长]]。正是Hines曾于1966至1969年间在《[[异世奇人|异世奇人]]》中饰演的杰米·麦卡克里蒙(Jamie McCrimmon)激发了加巴顿女士的灵感，勾勒出了这部《外乡人》的剧情设定和男主角Jamie Fraser的人物设定。<ref name="Hines 2014">{{cite news|last=Ross|first=Robyn|date=2014-08-19|title=Exclusive: ''Doctor Who'' Alum to Guest-Star on ''Outlander''|url=http://www.tvguide.com/News/Outlander-Frazer-Hines-1085670.aspx|work=[[电视指南_(美国杂志)|TV Guide]]|accessdate=2014-09-17|archive-date=2014-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141221001503/http://www.tvguide.com/News/Outlander-Frazer-Hines-1085670.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

