=== 音乐 ===
音乐由{{link-en|比尔·麦克瑞利|Bear McCreary}}负责。主题曲是一首改编歌曲。曲调取自苏格兰民歌《[[斯凯岛船歌|斯凯岛船歌]]》("The Skye Boat Song")，歌词改编自[[罗伯特·路易斯·史蒂文森|罗伯特·路易斯·史蒂文森]]的诗歌《请为我唱首那不知所踪的孩子的歌曲吧》("Sing me a Song of a Lad that is Gone")。<ref>{{cite web|title=''Outlander'': Opening Title Sequence – Wait, Is That It?|url=http://www.threeifbyspace.net/2014/07/outlander-opening-title-sequence-wait-is-that-it/#.VATG50tU10h|accessdate=2014-09-01|date=July 2014|last=Conrad|first=Erin|publisher=ThreeIfBySpace.net|archive-date=2020-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216105604/https://www.threeifbyspace.net/2014/07/outlander-opening-title-sequence-wait-is-that-it/#.VATG50tU10h|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Comic Con 2014 Highlights|url=http://www.bearmccreary.com/blog/blog/films/comic-con-2014-highlights/#blog/blog/films/comic-con-2014-highlights/|accessdate=2014-09-01|date=2014-07-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808052251/http://www.bearmccreary.com/blog/blog/films/comic-con-2014-highlights/#blog/blog/films/comic-con-2014-highlights/|archivedate=2014-08-08|dead-url=no|publisher=BearMcCreary.com}}</ref>

